PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778198576
OL,3,CHantavirus cruise ship still days away
OL,4,Cfrom docking in Tenerife
OL,6,FThe boat left the shores of Cape Verde
OL,7,Fat 6.15pm UK time on Wednesday,
OL,8,FOceanwide Expeditions said, and is
OL,9,Festimated to arrive at the port of
OL,10,FGranadilla in Tenerife in the early
OL,11,Fhours of Sunday but this is subject to
OL,12,Fchange.
OL,14,FThe Foreign Office is arranging a
OL,15,Fcharter flight so the remaining
OL,16,FBritons on board the ship who are not
OL,17,Fdisplaying symptoms can be repatriated
OL,18,Fonce they dock in Tenerife.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778198576
OL,3,CHantavirus cruise ship still days away
OL,4,Cfrom docking in Tenerife
OL,6,FDr Maria Van Kerkhove, from the World
OL,7,FHealth Organisation (WHO), said two
OL,8,Fpatients ` known to include a Briton `
OL,9,Fremain in hospital in the Netherlands,
OL,10,Fand another Briton is in intensive
OL,11,Fcare in South Africa.
OL,13,FShe told a WHO press briefing: "I am
OL,14,Fvery happy to say the patient in South
OL,15,FAfrica is doing better, and the two
OL,16,Fpatients in the Netherlands we hear
OL,17,Fare stable. So that is actually very
OL,18,Fgood news."
OL,26,@uD@`OUzD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
