CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778198576
OL,3,CHantavirus cruise ship still days away
OL,4,Cfrom docking in Tenerife
OL,6,FThe WHO said morale has improved on
OL,7,Fboard since the ship started its
OL,8,Fjourney to Tenerife.
OL,10,FIt said two doctors are on board along
OL,11,Fwith infectious disease experts from
OL,12,Fthe WHO and the European Centre for
OL,13,FDisease Prevention and Control (ECDC),
OL,14,Fwho are conducting a medical
OL,15,Fassessment of all passengers and crew.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778198576
OL,3,CHantavirus cruise ship still days away
OL,4,Cfrom docking in Tenerife
OL,6,FWhile the risk to the public is low,
OL,7,FDr Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus,
OL,8,Fdirector-general of the WHO, said
OL,9,Fthere could be more cases due to the
OL,10,Fincubation period of the Andes virus `
OL,11,Fthe variant of hantavirus linked to
OL,12,Fthe outbreak.
OL,14,FThe WHO is not expecting the outbreak
OL,15,Fto be an epidemic, according to Dr
OL,16,FAbdirahman Mahamud, director at the
OL,17,Falert and response co-ordination
OL,18,Fdepartment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
