PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778198576
OL,3,CHantavirus cruise ship still days away
OL,4,Cfrom docking in Tenerife
OL,6,FHe highlighted a similar outbreak in
OL,7,FArgentina in 2018/19 which led to 34
OL,8,Fcases.
OL,10,FIt emerged earlier that seven British
OL,11,Fpeople disembarked from the ship mid-
OL,12,Fway through the cruise, along with a
OL,13,Fwoman who later died.
OL,15,FA total of 29 people left the ship
OL,16,Fwhen it docked in the remote South
OL,17,FAtlantic island of St Helena,
OL,18,Fincluding a Dutch woman who became
OL,19,Funwell during onward travel and died.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778198576
OL,3,CHantavirus cruise ship still days away
OL,4,Cfrom docking in Tenerife
OL,6,FThe woman was accompanying her
OL,7,Fhusband's body, which was being
OL,8,Frepatriated after he died on the ship
OL,9,Fon April 11.
OL,11,FOceanwide Expeditions said guests who
OL,12,Fdisembarked have been contacted.
OL,14,FOn Wednesday, the ECDC said everyone
OL,15,Fon board should be considered a "close
OL,16,Fcontact".
OL,18,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,19,Fannounced that two Britons who had
OL,20,Falready returned from the vessel are
OL,21,Fisolating at home.
OL,26,@wD@aOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
