CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778198576
OL,3,CHantavirus cruise ship still days away
OL,4,Cfrom docking in Tenerife
OL,6,FThese passengers flew back to the UK
OL,7,Fvia Johannesburg after getting off in
OL,8,FSt Helena.
OL,10,FSome 19 British nationals were listed
OL,11,Fas passengers on the MV Hondius, which
OL,12,Fwas sailing from Argentina to Cape
OL,13,FVerde, with four British crew members.
OL,15,FUK health experts said British
OL,16,Fpassengers on board will be asked to
OL,17,Fself-isolate in the UK for 45 days.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778198576
OL,3,CHantavirus cruise ship still days away
OL,4,Cfrom docking in Tenerife
OL,6,FAccording to the UKHSA, none of the
OL,7,FBritish citizens on board are
OL,8,Freporting symptoms but they are being
OL,9,Fclosely monitored.
OL,11,FAsked about the two British passengers
OL,12,Fwho have returned to the UK, Professor
OL,13,FRobin May, chief scientific officer at
OL,14,Fthe UKHSA, added that contact tracing
OL,15,Fis happening for anyone who may have
OL,16,Fsat next to them on the flight home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778198576
OL,3,CHantavirus cruise ship still days away
OL,4,Cfrom docking in Tenerife
OL,6,FThe outbreak, which has been linked to
OL,7,Fthree deaths, has been connected to a
OL,8,Fbirdwatching expedition in Argentina
OL,9,Fwhich two of the passengers went on
OL,10,Fbefore boarding the ship.
OL,12,FThree people were taken off the ship
OL,13,Fon Wednesday to the Netherlands for
OL,14,Ftreatment, including Mr Anstee.
OL,16,FThe Associated Press reported the
OL,17,FArgentine government's hypothesis is
OL,18,Fthat a Dutch couple contracted the
OL,19,Fvirus during a birdwatching outing in
OL,20,Fthe city of Ushuaia before boarding.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
